TRIM(
        NVL(t2.address_1,'') || ' ' ||
        NVL(t2.address_2,'') || ' ' ||
        NVL(t2.address_3,'') || ' ' ||
        NVL(t2.address_4,'') || ' ' ||
        NVL(t2.address_5,'') || ' ' ||
        NVL(t2.address_6,'')
    )

CASE t4.FK_GENERIC_DETASER
    WHEN '1'  THEN 'INSTITUTIONAL BANKING'
    WHEN '2'  THEN 'PROJECT FINANCE'
    WHEN '3'  THEN 'SCHEME'
    WHEN '4'  THEN 'LARGE ENTERPRISES'
    WHEN '5'  THEN 'MEDIUM ENTERPRISES'
    WHEN '6'  THEN 'SMALL ENTERPRISES'
    WHEN '7'  THEN 'PRIVATE'
    WHEN '8'  THEN 'STANDARD'
    WHEN '9'  THEN 'MASS'
    WHEN '10' THEN 'VIRTUAL'
    WHEN '11' THEN 'INTERNAL ACCOUNTS'
END
